 {"id":"bd-yx9r.6.1","title":"Complete runtime builder/state/reactor/local/spawn_blocking/deadline-monitor surfaces","description":"Port the missing runtime-side user-facing surfaces: builder/local runtime APIs, environment/config-driven setup, stored-task and handle tables, deadline monitors, sharded state, spawn_blocking, and reactor registration/backends in a form that ANSI C users can actually exercise.","design":"Treat this as the substrate for network, server, and higher-protocol stacks. Implementation may use profile-specific adapters, but semantics and diagnostics must remain explicit.","acceptance_criteria":"A. Public runtime APIs cover builder/local/reactor/blocking/deadline/state surfaces with documented profile behavior.\\nB. Unit and integration tests cover registration, wakeups, blocking pool handoff, deadline misses, and fail-closed unsupported-profile behavior.\\nC. Logged smoke scripts exercise at least one native reactor path and one deterministic/lab path.","notes":"This task is a major blocker for real networking/protocol parity.","status":"in_progress","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:24.627046422Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-14T02:38:14.843302694Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["crate-parity","reactor","runtime"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.6.1","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:26:56.170324638Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.6.1","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:26:56.988853706Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.6.1","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:26:57.785428563Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.6.1","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.6","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:24.627046422Z","created_by"